Title: Who You Think I Am
Writer: Camille Laurens (novel), Safy Nebbou (adaptation), Safy Nebbou (dialogue), Safy Nebbou (screenplay), Julie Peyr (adaptation), Julie Peyr (dialogue), Julie Peyr (screenplay)
Actors: Juliette Binoche, Nicole Garcia, François Civil, Marie-Ange Casta
Plot: Claire, a 50-year-old divorced teacher, creates a fake Facebook profile of a 24-year-old woman. She finds a photo of a pretty young blonde and uses it. She has created an entirely fictional character, but why?
